# {{ project_name }}

A Databricks Asset Bundle ETL project with DLT pipeline scaffolded by [dex](https://github.com/yarrib/dex).

## Setup

```bash
uv sync
```

## Project Structure

```
{{ project_name }}/
├── src/{{ project_name }}/    # Pipeline source code
{% if include_notebook %}├── notebooks/                 # Databricks notebooks
{% endif %}├── resources/                 # Pipeline definitions
├── tests/                     # Tests
├── databricks.yml             # Databricks Asset Bundle config
└── pyproject.toml             # Project config
```

## Development

```bash
# Run tests
uv run pytest

# Lint
uv run ruff check .

# Format
uv run ruff format .
```

## Deploy

```bash
# Deploy to dev (default target)
databricks bundle deploy

# Deploy to staging
databricks bundle deploy --target staging

# Run the pipeline update
databricks bundle run {{ project_name }}_pipeline

# Deploy to prod
databricks bundle deploy --target prod
```
